reviewText: I bought this for my sister-in-law.  She loved it and it arrived on time.

Saw this on a local PBS station.  It's wonderful! It'll make you laugh, it'll make you cry, it'll make you feel good all over, even if you're not Jewish, especially if you are. You'll probably learn a little about  Passover and some of the traditions associated with it. A program you'll  want to see over and over again, throughout the year, not just at Passover.
